M&M.name: M&M
M&M.description: M&M is an indica dominant hybrid strain (70% indica/30% sativa) created through an unknown combination of other hybrid strains. Named for the iconic candy, M&M packs a delicious flavor and soothing high that will have you soaring for hours and hours on end. Much like its namesake, this bud packs a sweet chocolately flavor with light touches of spicy skunk and woody pine. The aroma is on the heavier side of things, with a super skunky overtone that’s accented by woody pine and a touch of earthy chocolate. The M&M high will settle in a few minutes after your final exhale, filling your brain with an expansive happiness that pushes out any negative or racing thoughts. A light physical tingle accompanies this heady lift, filling your body with a deep relaxation that drops you into a heavy state of calm. In combination with its high 15-20% average THC level, these full-bodied effects make M&M a great choice for treating those suffering from conditions such as chronic pain, muscle spasms or cramps, chronic stress or anxiety and insomnia. This bud has hand-shaped super dense forest green nugs with thin orange hairs, dark amber undertones and a coating of frosty, amber-tinted white crystal trichomes.

M-Con.name: M-Con
M-Con.description: M-Con, also known as “Afrinomicon,” is an evenly balanced hybrid strain (50% indica/50% sativa) created through crossing the classic LA Confidential X Heirloom Malawi strains. The perfect well-balanced hybrid for any discerning patient, M-Con packs full-bodied effects that will have you feeling mentally lifted and physically relaxed for hours on end. You'll feel the mental effects first a few minutes after your final exhale as your brain is filled with a happy lift and a boost of creativity. You'll feel focused and ready to jump on any artistic task at hand or carry on conversations with friends and strangers alike. But you'd better hurry – an enveloping sense of calm comes next, filling both mind and body with a light sedation that will have you falling off the face of the planet if you're not careful with your dosage. Thanks to these effects and its high 17-19% average THC level, M-Con is often chosen to treat a variety of conditions including chronic pain, headaches or migraines, chronic stress and depression. This bud has a sweet and fruity woody pine flavor with a punch of sour lemony citrus upon exhale. The aroma is of sour skunky citrus with a spicy woody overtone that lingers long after your final toke. M-Con buds have oversized and heavy dark olive green pepper-shaped nugs with bright orange hairs and chunky purple-tinted white crystal trichomes.

M.I.L.F..name: M.I.L.F.
M.I.L.F..description: MILF is a sativa dominant hybrid (80% sativa/20% indica) strain created as a cross between the insanely powerful Trainwreck X White Widow strains. This potent bud has a THC level of up to 19% and a well-balanced combination of strong and penetrating indica and sativa effects. The MILF high starts with a physical relaxing effect that is first felt as a heavy indica feeling that weighs your head down and causes heavily droopy red eyes. You'll feel insanely uplifted with a sense of utter serenity and ease and a slight feeling of couch-lock and the munchies. The exact effects of the MILF high vary based on the breeder, but hold a common thread of heavy body effects and a cerebral high. Because of this powerful combination of effects, MILF is perfect for treating chronic stress or anxiety, mild to moderate cases of depression, nausea, and chronic pain. This bud has an aroma of earthy woody sage and a taste of sage with a hint of pungent earth and pine upon exhale that becomes more intense as you smoke. MILF buds have small airy leafy bright green pebble-shaped nugs with lots of twisty olive green leaves and a thick spattering of fiery orange hairs and sweet sticky resin.

M.O.A.B..name: M.O.A.B.
M.O.A.B..description: M.O.A.B., also known as “Mother of All Buds,” is a sativa dominant hybrid strain (80% sativa/20% indica) created through crossing the classic Hindu Kush X Blueberry X Blue Dream X Chem Dawg strains. This celebrity child brings on the potent high with a THC level that falls between 20-30% on average and a myriad of long-lasting effects. You'll feel a cerebral lift at the start of the high that fills you with a sense of tingly euphoria, erasing any negative or racing thoughts. This pure sense of happiness quickly turns stoney, leaving you hazy and unfocused as your mind soars higher and higher. A relaxing body high comes next, washing over you and dropping you into a state of couch-lock and slight sedation that won't affect your mental state. With these effects and its high THC level, M.O.A.B. is often chosen to treat those suffering from conditions such as headaches or migraines, depression, mood swings, nausea or appetite loss, glaucoma, and mood swings. This bud has a sweet berry diesel flavor with a rich spicy earthy exhale. The aroma is of spicy earth and fresh fruity berries with a notable hit of pungent diesel as the nugs are broken apart and burned. M.O.A.B. buds have small rounded minty green nugs with thick orange hairs and a coating of tiny frosty amber crystal trichomes.

M.T.F..name: M.T.F.
M.T.F..description: M.T.F. is also popularly known as Matanuska Thunder Fuck. It is a hybrid strain, which is recognized for being extremely potent for even the experienced marijuana user. Coming from Alaska, it smells quite musky with earthy undertones. But its taste is something that will keep you coming back for more, during the inhale the strain will leave a chocolaty aftertaste in your mouth for hours. As for the nugget itself, it is covered by icy white hairs that should remind you of its snowy homeland. After smoking the strain, the effects will kick in slowly and gradually, but then reaches a point where you will get a strong body buzz. Its dirty name gives you more than enough reason to stay clear of it if you are a first time medical marijuana user. But then again, it is excellent for patients suffering from a variety of medical conditions including migraines, stress, nausea, anxiety and even an upset stomach. But that is not all, as it is just as effective at calming a patient and can help individuals suffering from anorexia.

M1.name: M1
M1.description: M1 is a rare slightly indica dominant hybrid strain (55% indica/45% sativa) created through a backcross of the potent Titan OG. This bud may be hard to come by on your average market, but it's definitely a breeder and patient favorite thanks to its well balanced effects and insanely high THC level that bottoms out at about 22-23% on average. The M1 high starts with a lift of the spirits, infusing your mind with a sense of hazy euphoria that immediately erases any negative or racing thoughts. As your mind lifts, your body will begin into a deeply relaxing tingly state that leaves you totally couch-locked and immovable with a sharp pang of hunger. Thanks to these effects and its high THC level, M1 is said to be perfect for treating those suffering from conditions such as mood swings, appetite loss or nausea, chronic stress, and chronic pain. This bud has a super spicy and herbal flavor with a notable mouthful of pine upon exhale. The aroma is of woody earth and pine with a touch of spicy herbs that intensifies as the nugs are broken apart and burned. M1 buds have grape-shaped bright neon green nugs with lots of thin orange hairs and a coating of frosty sandy amber crystal trichomes.

M2.name: M2
M2.description: M2 is a 100% pure sativa strain created through crossing a variety of landraces, Sri Lankan X Original Thai Acapulco Gold X (South African X Original Haze) to be specific. Known for its super delicious flavor and surprisingly anxiety-free effects, M2 is perfect for any sativa lover who appreciates a classic high. This bud has a sweet and sour spicy lemony citrus flavor with a flowery and hazy exhale. The aroma is of earthy herbs with flowery haze and spicy sharp citrus that intensify the more that you toke. The M2 high comes rushing in almost as soon as you exhale, slamming into your mind with has been described as an intensely euphoric lift that's free of any anxiety whatsoever. You'll feel focused with a creative intensity and motivation that gets your running on any artistic or mental task at hand. From start to finish, you'll feel energized in both mind and body without feeling too frenzied. With these effects and its high 19-20% average THC level, M2 is the perfect wake-and-bake strain for treating chronic fatigue, ADD or ADHD, depression, chronic stress and mood swings. This bud has long tapered spade-shaped forest green nugs with thin orange hairs and a coating of frosty blue-tinted white crystal trichomes.

M7.name: M7
M7.description: M7 is an evenly balanced hybrid strain (50% indica/50% sativa) created through crossing the classic Master OG X Sour Diesel strains. Although hard to find on your average market, M7 is often sought after for its insanely high 19-25% average THC level and powerful effects that are perfect for any hybrid lover. The high starts with a lifted effect that launches through your mind with a sense of pure euphoria and ease, filling you with creative energy and motivation that lends itself well to any artistic task that you have at hand. As your mind lifts higher and higher, a touch of motivation will settle in, giving you the oomph that you need to take on your to-do list with ease. With these long-lasting effects and its high THC level, M7 is often chosen to treat those suffering from conditions such as mood swings, chronic stress, depression, chronic fatigue, and nausea. M7 has a fresh sweet and sour diesel flavor with a hint of skunky earth and herbs upon exhale. The aroma is of earthy diesel and skunky herbs with a touch of spicy sour pine as the nugs are broken apart and burned. M7 buds have oversized dense spade-shaped bright neon green nugs with vivid orange hairs and a coating of chunky amber crystal trichomes.

M8 Blue.name: M8 Blue
M8 Blue.description: M8 Blue is a 100% pure sativa strain that is said to be a landrace from unknown regions. A favorite in Northern California, M8 Blue packs a gorgeous appearance and an energizing high that will have you feeling fine from head to toe. Like its name suggests, M8 Blue has super fat and heavy oversized pepper-shaped olive green nugs with bright blue undertones, thin orange hairs and a coating of tiny, milky blue-tinted crystal trichomes. As you pull apart each sticky little nugget, aromas of fruity chemicals and sour, lemony citrus are released, intensifying in potency the more that you toke. The flavor is on the sweeter side of the spectrum, with a sugary strawberry taste accented by sour lemony citrus and earthy herbs. The M8 Blue high will hit you almost as soon as you experience your first tasty exhale, rushing into your mind with a lifted sense of giddy energy. Your mind will feel stimulated with a light tingly sense that serves to numb the brain rather than to activate it. While your euphoria grows to endless heights, a sharp pang of hunger will overtake your body, leaving you reaching for anything and everything in sight to quell your uncontrollable munchies. Thanks to these effects and its high 20-23% average THC level, M8 Blue is often chosen to treat those suffering from conditions such as chronic stress or anxiety, depression, chronic fatigue, headaches or migraines and chronic pain.

MAC1.name: MAC1
MAC1.description: MAC 1, also known as “Miracle Alien Cookies X1.” Is an evenly balanced hybrid strain (50% indica/50% sativa) created as a backcross of the iconic MAC strain. MAC 10.name: MAC 10

MAC Burger.name: MAC Burger
MAC Burger.description: MAC Burger, also known as “M.A.C. Burger,” is an evenly balanced hybrid strain (50% indica/50% sativa) created through crossing the iconic (MAC X Tropicana Cookies) X Donny Burger strains. Machine gun.name: Machine gun
Machine gun.description: Machine Gun, also known as “Machine Gun Funk,” is a sativa dominant hybrid strain created through a four-way cross of the infamous Pure Haze X Skunk X G-13 X AK Confidential strains. With a powerful 22% average THC level and a funky flavor, Machine Gun is one hard-hitter that you'll want in your arsenal. The high of Machine Gun is just as funky as the flavor, with long-lasting effects that hit you like a freight train and just won't quit for hours on end. Maclato.name: Maclato
Maclato.description: Maclato, also known as “MAC Lato” or “MAClato,” is an indica dominant hybrid strain (70% indica/30% sativa) created through crossing the classic Gelato X Grape MAC strains. The perfect celebrity child for any high-powered indica lover, Maclato packs a punch of delicious flavors and effects. This bud has oversized and heavy hand-shaped bright emerald-green nugs with dark purple undertones, orange hairs and a coating of tiny, white crystal trichomes.

Mac N Cookies.name: Mac N Cookies
Mac N Cookies.description: Mac'N Cookies, also known as “Mac N Cookies,” is an evenly balanced hybrid strain (50% indica/50% sativa) created through crossing the classic Miracle Alien Cookies (MAC) X Alien Cheese strains. Famous for its unique yet super delicious flavor, Mac'N Cookies is perfect for any hybrid lover who loves a high level of potency to their medicine. MAC N Jack.name: MAC N Jack
MAC N Jack.description: MAC N Jack is an evenly balanced hybrid strain (50% indica/50% sativa) created through crossing the potent MAC1 X Jack Herer strains. Mad Max.name: Mad Max
Mad Max.description: Mad Max, also known as “Mad Max #33,” is a slightly sativa dominant hybrid strain (60% sativa/40% indica) created through crossing the classic Amnesia Haze X Top44 strains. If you're after a well-balanced hybrid with effects that will have you feeling energized and outgoing, Mad Max is the perfect choice for you. The high hits you fast and hard, filling your brain with a lifted sense that increases your energy levels exponentially while also infusing you with increased sociability. This bud has a sour citrusy flavor with a lightly flowery and hazy exhale that intensifies in spiciness the more that you continue to toke. Mad Max buds have small rounded olive green nugs with thin red-orange hairs and a coating of tiny, amber white crystal trichomes.

Madness.name: Madness
Madness.description: Madness is a 100% indica hybrid strain created through crossing the classic Bubba Kush X G-13 strains. Madness buds have lumpy light minty green spade-shaped nugs with lots of furry orange hairs and a dusting of tiny milky white crystal trichomes.

Magic Dragon.name: Magic Dragon

Magic Johnson.name: Magic Johnson

Magic Mango.name: Magic Mango

Magic Melon.name: Magic Melon

Magic Merlin.name: Magic Merlin

Magic Night.name: Magic Night

Thanks to these effects and its low 0-1% THC level and super high 15-22% average CBD level, Magic Potion is often chosen to treat a wide variety of conditions including inflammation, chronic pain, seizures or epilepsy, cramps or muscle spasms and the effects of PMS. This bud has a sweet and spicy flowery sage flavor with a sour lemon-lime exhale. The aroma is very similar, with a citrusy lemon-lime overtone accented by spicy herbs and fresh earthiness. Magic Potion buds have airy spade-shaped forest green nugs with deep purple undertones, thick orange hairs and frosty, dark amber crystal trichomes.

Magilla Gorilla.name: Magilla Gorilla
Magilla Gorilla.description: Magilla Gorilla is an indica dominant hybrid strain (65% indica/35% sativa) created through crossing the potent Grape Ape X Space Ghost strains. If you're after a super relaxing high that will help prime you to get the best sleep of your life, you've found it with Magilla Gorilla. This bud boosts the spirits and soothes the body before gently helping you fade away into a long-lasting and peaceful sleep. You'll feel lifted from start to finish with this bud, free of both mental and physical aches or pains. An overall calm will accompany this high, too, helping you really kick back before you finally fall into a heavy sedation. These sleepy effects combined with its super high 15-20% average THC level make Magilla Gorilla a great choice for treating those suffering from conditions such as insomnia, chronic pain, cramps or muscle spasms, arthritis and spasticity. This bud has a classic sour yet sweet fruity citrus flavor with a lightly savory berry diesel exhale. The aroma is of spicy diesel with a light touch of earthy herbs and sweet fruity berries galore. Magilla Gorilla buds have small rounded forest green nugs with deep purple undertones, thin orange hairs and a coating of tiny clear crystal trichomes.

Magna Rosa.name: Magna Rosa
Magna Rosa.description: Magna Rosa, also known as “Manga Rosa,” is a 100% pure sativa strain that is native to the Brazilian regions. Known for its long-lasting and heady high, Magna Rosa is the perfect bud for when you need a quick kick of energy to get you up and moving. You'll feel an instant influx of cerebral energy that gets you moving and focused on anything and everything on your to-do list. This is accompanied by a sense of pure euphoria that lasts for hours and hours on end without relief. Thanks to these effects and its high 15-21% average THC level, Magna Rosa is often said to be perfect for treating those suffering from conditions such as headaches or migraines, glaucoma or eye pressure, chronic fatigue, depression and chronic stress. This bud has a classic sweet and spicy tropical citrus flavor with a notable punch of mango upon exhale. The aroma is of spicy herbs and sour tropical citrus with an earthy overtone that lingers long after the nugs are burned away. Magna Rosa buds have fat long bright neon green nugs with reddish-orange hairs and a coating of chunky frosty white crystal trichomes that are practically dripping with sweet syrupy resin.

Magnum OG.name: Magnum OG
Magnum OG.description: Magnum, also known as “Magnum OG,” is an evenly balanced hybrid (50% indica/50% sativa) strain that is a blend of Ruderalis X Indica X Sativa, although the exact parent strains are unknown. Even with the lack of information about this bud, it is thought to be a member of the OG Kush family and maybe the AK-47, although neither can be confirmed. The Magnum high is said to be perfect for quelling social anxieties when getting ready for a night out with friends. It gives you a euphoric boost that's perfect for giving you social energy and encouraging interaction and laughter with anyone and everyone around you. This state won't cause you anxiety, as the THC level of this bud is generally pretty low, topping out at about 15%, and you will feel calm throughout the duration of the high. With these effects, Magnum is often chosen by patients suffering from chronic stress, insomnia, depression, and glaucoma. This bud has an appearance that's actually very underwhelming – it has long piecey leafy olive green nugs with sparse light amber hairs and matching trichomes. Even with the disappointing appearance, the flavor and aroma make up for all of it – it has a sweet floral effect that's accented by fresh pine and earth for a smooth sweet smoke that is perfect every time.

Magnum Opus F2.name: Magnum Opus F2
Magnum Opus F2.description: Magnum Opus F2 is an evenly balanced hybrid strain (50% indica/50% sativa) created through crossing the powerful Magnum Opus X Magnum Opus strains. The perfect potent hybrid for a day when you have things to do but not much to focus on, Magnum Opus F2 packs high-powered effects and a high level of potency into each and every toke. The high comes on with a rush of effects, filling your brain with an instant sense of lifted euphoria and cerebral energy. You'll be sociable and outgoing in this state, easily chatting with friends and strangers alike for hours on end. At the same time, a light sense of relaxation will wash over your body, helping to keep you anchored. With these effects and its high 20-30% average THC level, Magnum Opus F2 is often chosen to treat a variety of conditions including chronic pain, depression or mood swings, chronic stress or PTSD and chronic fatigue. This bud has a sweet and fruity flowery grape flavor with hints of rich anise upon exhale. The aroma is very similar, with an earthy herbal overtone accented by spicy flowers and sweet fruity grapes. Magnum Opus F2 buds have fluffy spade-shaped olive green nugs with bright purple undertones, dark amber hairs and a coating of dark amber crystal trichomes.

Mail Order Bride.name: Mail Order Bride
Mail Order Bride.description: Mail Order Bride is a super rare indica dominant hybrid strain created through crossing the just as rare Bubba Love X Taskenti strains. When you find this gorgeous lady, you better snap her up ASAP before someone else comes along and takes her home. Mail Order Bride brings heavy-hitting nighttime effects that are fueled by a powerful THC level that bottoms out at about 20% on average and can hit as high as 29%. And with its sweet minty lemon flavor, you'll be hard-pressed to find someone who won't want a piece of this Mail Order Bride. The aroma is just as addicting, with a hashy coffee effect that's accented by tangy lemon and a kick of sharp menthol that's surprisingly sweet smelling. And the high? You'll immediately fall in love. The Mail Order Bride high starts with a creeping effect that slowly sneaks up on you before taking hold of your entire body and dropping you into a deeply sedative state of complete couch-lock. As your body melts into wherever you happen to be sitting, a buzzing effect will wash over you, slowly pulling you down into a deep and peaceful sleep. With these heavy effects, Mail Order Bride is the perfect nighttime choice for those suffering from chronic pain, depression, muscle spasms, and insomnia. This bud has gorgeous heavy dense bright neon green nugs with sparse orange hairs and a dusting of clear trichomes that sometimes have a slightly gold tint to them, making for one beautiful lady all the way around.

Mai Tai.name: Mai Tai
Mai Tai.description: Mai Tai is an evenly balanced hybrid strain (50% indica/50% sativa) created through a delicious cross of the potent Maui Waui X Tutti Frutti strains. Love a great Mai Tai? This bud brings the best of its insanely delicious flavor to a super lifted full-bodied high, creating the perfect recipe for a lazy afternoon spent with friends or family. You'll feel an almost immediately energetic onset, buzzing through your mind like an electrical current and leaving you feeling euphoric, lifted and pretty sociable and outgoing. As you find yourself dropping into deep conversation with those around you, a heavily sedative body buzz will creep over your physical form, leaving you deeply relaxed and immovable. Combined with its super high 26-32% average THC level, these effects make Mai Tai perfect for treating chronic pain, depression, chronic stress, inflammation and cramps or muscle spasms. Mai Tai has a sweet and citrusy tropical fruity flavor with a touch of sharp mint to it, too. The aroma is just as delicious, with a fruity berry overtone accented by sweet and sour citrus and sharp flowery mint. Mai Tai buds have fluffy dense oversized bright neon green nugs with golden amber undertones, orange hairs and a coating of golden amber crystal trichomes.

Mai Tai Cookies.name: Mai Tai Cookies
Mai Tai Cookies.description: Mai Tai Cookies is a sativa dominant hybrid strain created through crossing the delicious Alien Orange Cookies X ACDC strains. This bud took home 1st Place for Best CBD Flower at the 2016 High Times Cannabis Cup in Los Angeles, and for good reason. With a powerful CBD level that typically bottoms out at about 12%, a moderate THC level of 8-14%, and a myriad of uplifting mellow effects, Mai Tai Cookies has definitely earned that title! The Mai Tai Cookies high starts with a euphoric boost of uplifted energy that infuses you with a sense of focus and motivation that's not overwhelming. As your mind tackles any task you put forward, your body will fall into a deeply relaxing state that can be slightly sedative at times. In combination with its high CBD level, these effects give Mai Tai Cookies a distinct advantage in treating a variety of conditions including headaches or migraines, chronic pain, fatigue, and depression, among others. This bud has a sweet tangy cherry flavor with a sharp citrus exhale. The aroma is of earthy sweet citrus with a surprisingly strong hint of cherry. Mai Tai Cookies buds have super dense and chunky light minty green nugs with a super frosty coating of bright white crystal trichomes.

Malana.name: Malana
Malana.description: Malana, also known as “Pure Highland Sativa Chavras,” is a rare 100% sativa strain that is native to the Malana Village in the Himachal Pradesh region of Northern India. This beautiful bud packs a bright and heady high that's perfect for a wake-and-bake when you just can't seem to get up and going. You'll feel almost instantly energized with a vibrant cerebral effect that has you feeling creative and in an almost frenzied state. This is accompanied by a giggly sense that has you laughing at anything and everything around you before you fade completely away into psychedelic thought and visions. With these effects and its high 10-25% average THC level, Malana is often chosen to treat those suffering from conditions such as chronic fatigue, depression, chronic stress, migraines or headaches and eye pressure or glaucoma. This bud has a sweet fruity mango flavor with a rich creamy caramel exhale. The aroma is of sweet toffee and spicy florals with a fruity overtone that becomes more and more sugary as the nugs are broken apart and burned. Malana buds have super sticky oversized rock-hard spade-shaped nuggets that are bright neon green in color with spatterings of vivid orange hairs throughout.

Malawi Gold.name: Malawi Gold
Malawi Gold.description: Malawi Gold is a 100% pure sativa strain native to the region of Malawi in Africa that is a favorite of breeders and users alike. This classic bud offers a moderate THC level between 9-13% and a mild aroma of banana, as it is traditionally cured wrapped in layers of banana leaves. Malawi Gold is prized among cannabis users for its uplifting clear-headed high that won't weight you down or leave you feeling anxious or paranoid. This high hits you fast with a crashing wave of cerebral energy that leaves you laser-focused with a sense of motivation and purpose. Because of its moderate THC level, the cerebral effects are not too overpowering and are perfect for any level of cannabis user. Because of these cerebral sativa effects, Malawi Gold is often a choice for treating fatigue, mild cases of depression, chronic stress, and nausea. This bud has pyramid-shaped bright neon green super leafy nugs with red hairs and frosty amber hued trichomes and sweet sticky resin. Malawi Gold has a classic sativa aroma of sweet and spicy fresh herbs with just a hint of banana and an enticing taste of sweet and spicy herbal tea with just a touch of earth upon exhale.

Malibu Pure Kush.name: Malibu Pure Kush
Malibu Pure Kush.description: Malibu Pure Kush, not to be confused with “Pure Kush,” is a rare indica dominant hybrid strain created as a phenotype of the infamous OG Kush, although the breeders keep its exact heritage as a closely guarded secret. Malibu Pure Kush is a local strain to the Malibu region and is infamous for its classic flavor and effects. Malibu Pure Kush as a rich sweet and sour woody pine flavor with hints of sharp citrus and eye-opening mint upon exhale. The aroma takes a slightly pungent herbal turn, with rich earthy citrus and sharp menthol released as the nugs are burned. The Malibu Pure Kush high is just as addictive as the flavor, with classic effects that are peaceful and uplifting throughout the duration of the high. You'll feel peaceful and lifted throughout, with a clear mind and relaxed body. Thanks to these effects and its super high 18-29% average THC level, Malibu Pure Kush is said to be perfect for treating conditions such as depression, mood swings, chronic fatigue, depression, ADD or ADHD, and chronic stress or anxiety. This bud has fluffy piecey bright neon green nugs with fiery orange hairs and a coating of sparkling amber crystal trichomes.

Malonica.name: Malonica
Malonica.description: Malonica is a sativa dominant hybrid strain (75% sativa/25% indica) created through an unknown combination of hybrid strains. On the hunt for a great wake-and-bake strain for a weekend morning afternoon when you have plans later in the day? This bud is totally made for you. The high comes on fast and hard with a rush of cerebral effects that instantly boost your energy and your spirits, filling you with a giddy euphoria that gets you up and out of bed or off of the couch in no time at all. With these effects and its high 18-25% average THC level, Malonica is often chosen to treat those suffering from conditions such as chronic fatigue, depression, chronic stress, appetite loss or nausea and headaches or migraines. Malverde.name: Malverde
Malverde.description: Malverde, also known as “Mexican Survivor,” is a heavily sativa dominant hybrid strain (90% sativa/10% indica or 95% sativa/5% indica) with unknown parentage but is said to be a strain native to the Michoacán regions of Mexico. This bud is best known for its delicious flavor, which is said to be like enjoying a fresh margarita, with tastes of sweet and sour citrus accented by fresh lemon and lime and just a touch of spice. The aroma is just as delicious, with a spicy citrus overtone and sweet lemon-lime scents galore. The Malverde high is one that will have you feeling just as happy as if you've enjoyed a margarita, with uplifting and energizing effects that hit fast and hard, almost as soon as you exhale. You'll feel energized with a sense of creative motivation that's perfect for jumping on any artistic task that you may have at hand. A light tingly physical sense accompanies this heady lift, getting your muscles moving and you up and off the couch. These effects combined with its super high 28-29% average THC level make Malverde perfect for treating experienced patients suffering from chronic fatigue, depression, chronic stress or PTSD and appetite loss or nausea. This bud has fluffy spade-shaped dark olive green nugs with amber undertones, bright orange hairs and frosty purple-tinted white crystal trichomes.

Mamasan.name: Mamasan
Mamasan.description: Mamasan is a 100% pure indica hybrid strain with unknown parentage that was originally grown in the mountains of Colorado. Even with the lack of information about its heritage, Mamasan is a favorite of breeders and patients alike thanks to its full-bodied relaxing effects and super easy grow. The high starts with a subtle boost of the spirits, filling your mind with a lifted sense of happiness and ease. You'll find yourself slowly fading in and out of focus as your mental state reaches new levels of bliss. Your body will begin to follow suit, fading into a sense of deep calm that has you totally couch-locked and immovable before dropping you off into a purely sedative and sleepy state. With these heavy effects and its high 17-19% average THC level, Mamasan is said to be perfect for treating conditions such as chronic pain, depression, insomnia and chronic stress or PTSD. This bud has a sweet fruity pine flavor with a lightly skunky and spicy exhale. The aroma is of earthy herbs and woods with a heavy skunky pungency to it that intensifies the more that you toke. Mamasan buds have fat rounded spade-shaped neon green nugs with lots of light orange hairs and a coating of frosty tiny white crystal trichomes.

Mama Thai.name: Mama Thai
Mama Thai.description: Mama Thai is a 100% pure sativa strain that is a native landrace found throughout the regions of Thailand. Known for its strong cerebral high and psychedelic nature, Mama Thai is highly recommended for lovers of high-powered sativas who don’t suffer from anxiety or paranoia when they toke. Mama Thai buds have skinny airy forest green nugs with minty green undertones, matching leaves, thin dark orange hairs and a coating of frosty chunky white crystal trichomes.

ManBearPig.name: ManBearPig
ManBearPig.description: ManBearPig, also known as “Man Bear Pig” or “ManBearPig OG,” is a slightly sativa dominant hybrid strain (60% sativa/40% indica) created through crossing the powerful Animal Cookies X Lemon OG strains. Named for the iconic character in South Park, ManBearPig packs a punch of legendary effects that hit both mind and body for hours on end. ManBearPig buds have oversized spade-shaped dense neon green nugs with thin yellow-orange hairs and a coating of chunky white crystal trichomes.

Mandarin Confectionery.name: Mandarin Confectionery
Mandarin Confectionery.description: Mandarin Confectionery is a sativa dominant hybrid strain (70% sativa/30% indica) created through crossing the iconic California Black Rose X Mandarin Sunset strains. A vibrant bud with an electrifying high, Mandarin Confectionery is the perfect sativa to get you out of bed in the morning with a smile on your face. Mandarin Glue.name: Mandarin Glue
Mandarin Glue.description: Mandarin Glue is a sativa dominant hybrid strain (85% sativa/15% indica) created through crossing the classic NYC Diesel Mandarin Cut X Original Glue strains. Mandarin Mints.name: Mandarin Mints
Mandarin Mints.description: Mandarin Mints, also known as “Mandarin Cookies,” is a rare sativa dominant hybrid (70% sativa/30% indica) strain created through crossing the classic Tangerine Power X Girl Scout Cookies Thin Mint strains. In combination with its super high 27-28% average THC level, these effects give Mandarin Mints an edge in treating conditions such as chronic fatigue, depression, migraines or headaches, inflammation, nausea, and chronic pain. This bud has thin neon green nugs with long amber hairs and a coating of bright amber crystal trichomes.

Mandarin Sunset.name: Mandarin Sunset
Mandarin Sunset.description: Mandarin Sunset is a perfect strain choice for those of you looking to replicate a smell similar to that of Cuties Clementine. This medicinal marijuana strain carries effects are long lasting and provides a sufficient buzz.

Mandarin Zkittlez.name: Mandarin Zkittlez

Mandy's Dream.name: Mandy's Dream
Mandy's Dream.description: Mandy's Dream is a rare evenly balanced hybrid (50% indica/50% sativa) strain created through crossing the classic Mandarin Kush with the infamous Blue Dream strain. This bud has a classic sweet citrusy blueberry flavor and an earthy herbal aroma to match. Mandy's Dream buds have small round bluish green nugs with purple undertones, lots of long thin orange hairs, and a coating of super frosty bright white tiny crystal trichomes.]

Mandy Purple.name: Mandy Purple
Mandy Purple.description: Mandy Purple, also known as “Mandarin Purple,” is an indica dominant hybrid strain created through crossing the classic Tangerine Kush with an unknown purple strain. This bud packs an insanely addictive flavor that blends together the best of both purple and orange strains, with a super spicy grape and citrus flavor that drips off of your tongue. The Mandy Purple high isn't quite as eye-opening as the flavor, but it does pack a pretty potent punch. Mango Berry.name: Mango Berry

Over the next few minutes, the high will spread throughout the rest of your body in warming waves, leaving you lazy, couch-locked, and completely sedated. Because of these effects and its up to 20% THC level, Mango Berry is perfect for treating a variety of conditions, including inflammation, chronic stress or anxiety, nausea, and appetite loss. Mango Crush.name: Mango Crush
Mango Crush.description: Mango Crush is a super rare sativa dominant hybrid strain created through an unknown combination of sativa-dominant tropical strains. Mango Durban.name: Mango Durban
Mango Durban.description: Mango Durban, also known as “Durban Mango,” is a 100% pure sativa strain created through crossing the delicious Mangobiche X Durban strains. Mango G-13.name: Mango G-13
Mango G-13.description: Mango G-13, also known as “Mango G13” or “G-13 Mango,” is an evenly balanced hybrid strain (50% indica/50% sativa) created through crossing the classic Mango Haze X G-13 strains.
