This bud has a super sweet and fruity tropical mango flavor with a lightly sour and citrusy exhale. The aroma is very similar, with a spicy diesel overtone accented by a punch of sharply sour pineapple and mango. Mango G-13 buds have fat and fluffy popcorn-shaped minty green nugs with thin orange hairs and a coating of frosty milky golden white crystal trichomes.

Mangolian Indica.name: Mangolian Indica
Mangolian Indica.description: Mangolian Indica, not to be confused with “Mongolian,” is a rare 100% pure indica hybrid strain created as a cross of the infamous Afghan Skunk X Afghani X Northern Lights #5 strains. This bud took home the bronze medal at the 2005 HighLife Cup in Amsterdam, snagging 3rd Place overall for Best Indica. Mangolian Indica packs all of the classic flavors and effects of your favorite indica strains into one tasty little bud. It has a sweet flavor of fresh mine and lemon with a touch of sage and mint upon exhale. The aroma is very fresh and herby with a floral overtone that has a touch of fresh mango that can be detected as the nugs are broken apart. Mangolian Indica buds have leafy brownish red nugs with long thin amber hairs and a coating of sandy amber colored crystal trichomes. The Mangolian Indica high packs relaxing and lethargic effects that are long-lasting and best suited for late night when you need a little help sleeping. The high comes on with a creeping effect, building its way into your mind before pulling you down into sleepy introspection and hazy waking dreams. As your mind falls further and further, your body will follow suit, ending with a deep and peaceful nap that can last for hours. In combination with its high 10-16% average THC level, these effects make Mangolian Indica perfect for treating chronic stress, depression, insomnia, chronic fatigue, and migraines.

Mango Mac.name: Mango Mac
Mango Mac.description: Mango Mac is a super rare sativa dominant hybrid strain created through crossing Mango Kush with the classic AMG Haze strain. This bud is hard to find on your average market, but is infamous for its mouthwateringly delicious mango flavor and bright cheery effects. Mango Mac has a flavor of your classic haze strain that has been dropped into a bowl of fresh ripe mangos. The aroma is just as addictive with a tropical spicy overtone that plays well with the sweet ripe mango. Almost as soon as you finish you first smooth fruity exhale, your mind will start to succumb to the effects of Mango Mac, lifting into a state of happiness that is stimulating and euphoric. You'll find yourself drifting into a hazy giggly state soon after that leaves you spacey and distant, although still sociable at times. Thanks to these heady effects and its high 15-16% average THC level, Mango Mac is often chosen to treat conditions such as chronic pain, depression, fatigue, migraines or headaches, nausea, and glaucoma. This bud has small piecey bright neon green nugs with long thin orange hairs and a coating of bright amber crystal trichomes.

Mango Punch.name: Mango Punch
Mango Punch.description: Mango Punch is an indica dominant hybrid strain (70% indica/30% sativa) created through crossing the delicious Mango X another unknown hybrid strain. Although it has never been confirmed officially, many seem to agree that the likely second parent of Mango Punch is, in fact, the beloved Purple Punch strain. Nonetheless, if you're after a sweet and fruity bud with a soothing nighttime high, you've found it with Mango Punch. This bud packs a head-spinning flavor of fresh juicy mangoes accented by sour citrusy pineapple and tropical tree fruits. The aroma is just as vibrant, with a sweet mango overtone accented by citrusy pineapple and sweet tropical fruits. The Mango Punch high will slam into your brain almost as soon as you exhale, launching your mind into a lifted state of focus and motivation. But you'd better hurry – this focus will soon disappear, replaced with pure sleepy sedation that can have you feeling pretty stoned at times. Thanks to these effects and its high 18-24% average THC level, Mango Punch is often chosen to treat a variety of conditions such as arthritis, depression or mood swings, chronic stress or PTSD, headaches or migraines and chronic pain. This bud has super dense and small triangle-shaped emerald green nugs with furry orange hairs, golden undertones and frosty matching crystal trichomes.

Mango Sherbet.name: Mango Sherbet
Mango Sherbet.description: Mango Sherbet, also known as “Mango Sherbert,” is an indica dominant hybrid strain crated through a delicious cross of Mango Trees X Mango Kush X Sherbet. Best known for its insanely tasty flavor, Mango Sherbet brings on the mouthwatering tastes, with hints of sugary berries and fresh sweet mango with a rich tropical overtone. The aroma follows the same profile, although with a touch of earthiness to it as well. The Mango Sherbet high isn't quite as bright as the flavor, with effects that are mentally stimulating yet physically relaxing in nature. It starts with a relaxing cerebral build in the back of the head, tingly and slightly numbing. You'll feel an influx of creative energy and focus just before your body drops away into a heavy, long-lasting physical high. A touch of the giggles comes next, leaving you laughing at anything and everything around you with ease. Thanks to these effects and its super high 24-28% average THC level, Mango Sherbet is often chosen to treat those suffering from chronic pain, cramps or muscle spasms, chronic stress or anxiety and chronic fatigue. This bud has fluffy rounded forest green nugs with long thin orange hairs and a frosty thick coating of tiny dusty amber crystal trichomes.

Mango Taffy.name: Mango Taffy
Mango Taffy.description: Mango Taffy, more commonly known as “MangoTaffie,” is a slightly indica dominant hybrid strain (60% indica/40% sativa) created through crossing the delicious Mango Kush X Taffie strains. With this bud, the name says it all in the flavor department. Mango Taffy packs a super sweet tropical mango flavor with hints of sour citrus and light spices, too. The aroma is very similar, with an herbal woody effect that turns spicy and citrusy as the nugs are broken apart and burned away. The Mango Taffy high settles in a few minutes after your final toke, starting with a slow build of euphoric energy. You'll feel an influx of focus and sociability that lends itself well to conversations with friends and family alike. A touch of creativity accompanies this focused motivation, which can get you moving on any artistic task that you may have at hand. A touch of physical relaxation will keep you anchored throughout this lifted high without causing you to feel sedated in the slightest. With these effects and its high 18-22% average THC level and 2-3% CBD level, Mango Taffy is often chosen to treat conditions such as chronic pain, depression, chronic stress or anxiety and chronic fatigue. This bud has oversized fluffy spade-shaped bright neon green nugs with thin orange hairs and a coating of frosty golden amber crystal trichomes.

Mango Trainwreck.name: Mango Trainwreck
Mango Trainwreck.description: Mango Trainwreck is an evenly balanced hybrid strain (50% indica/50% sativa) created through a deliciously potent cross of Mango Kush X Trainwreck strains. Insanely delicious flavors and hard-hitting effects combine for the ultimate celebrity child in this potent bud. Mango Trainwreck brings together the best of both of its parents, all wrapped up with a super potent 22-29% average THC level. The Mango Trainwreck high comes on with a rush of cerebral energy, slamming into your head almost as soon as you exhale, lifting your mind into a pure euphoric state that is super relaxing in nature. As your mind settles, your body will begin to fade away into a heavily sedative physical high that leaves you hopelessly couch-locked and ravenously hungry, reaching for anything and everything in sight to snack on. This effect quickly turns sleepy, leaving you dozing on and off as you settle into a state of pure peace and happiness. Thanks to these heavy effects and its high THC level, Mango Trainwreck is said to be perfect for treating conditions such as nausea or appetite loss, chronic stress, migraines or headaches, chronic fatigue, and chronic pain. This bud has spade-shaped fluffy olive green nugs with dark orange hairs and a coating of frosty tiny white crystal trichomes.

Manna.name: Manna
Manna.description: Manna is a rare evenly balanced hybrid strain (50% indica/50% sativa) created through crossing the infamous Jack Herer X Allen Wrench strains. Perfect for any patient who loves a delicious flavor and a potent high, Manna packs a punch of well-balanced effects that hit both mind and body with a high level of power that lasts for hours and hours on end. The high starts with a lifted effect that fills your cerebral state with a sense of euphoria and a touch of relaxation. This effect will quickly begin to spread throughout the rest of your body, dropping you into a slightly couch-locked state that can leave you feeling ravenously hungry, too. In combination with its high 23% average THC level, these effects give Manna the perfect edge in treating those suffering from conditions such as nausea, chronic fatigue, depression, chronic pain, and chronic stress. This bud has a sweet tropical pineapple flavor with a hint of sour cherry candies upon exhale. The aroma is of fresh earthy fruits with a sour tropical overtone that's accented by rich berries and spices. Manna buds have airy neon forest green nugs with rich gold undertones, amber hairs, and a coating of sparkling crystal trichomes.

Man O War.name: Man O War
Man O War.description: Man O War, also known as “Man ‘O War,” is a slightly sativa dominant hybrid strain (60% sativa/40% indica) created through crossing the powerful Bruce Banner #3 X Alien Rift #6 strains. The perfect bud for a lazy day spent at home when you may have some stuff to get done, Man O War packs an energizing and stimulating high that's bright and happy. The high comes on quickly, first electrifying your mind with a blissful heady lift that's accompanied by a warming tingly feeling in the back of the head and neck. This tingle will soon work its way throughout the rest of your body, slipping into your limbs and leaving them feeling lightly energized but totally relaxed from head to toe. This effect isn't sedative but rather will help ease away aches and pains to get you up and moving and ready to clean, go for a walk or just settle in for a conversation with friends. Combined with its high 15-18% average THC level, these effects give Man O War an edge in treating conditions such as chronic fatigue, depression, chronic stress, headaches or migraines and nausea or appetite loss. This bud has a classic sour citrus flavor with hints of fruity blueberries, too. The aroma is of fresh ripe blueberries with a touch of spicy yet sour citrusy lemon. Man O War buds have fat popcorn-shaped minty green nugs with lots of thin orange hairs and a coating of tiny milky white trichomes.

Mantis.name: Mantis
Mantis.description: Mantis is a rare evenly balanced hybrid strain (50% indica/50% sativa) created through crossing the classic Nap X (Santa Maria X Haze) strains. Perfect for any hybrid lover, Mantis brings on a full-bodied high that will lift you up before helping you slowly settle down and get to sleep after the most stressful of days or weeks. The high starts a few minutes after your final toke, hitting the brain first. You'll feel a light lift of the spirits that turns into full-blown euphoria, pushing out any negative or racing thoughts immediately. As your reach new heights of happiness, you'll feel your limbs begin to relax with a soothing physical high. This combination quickly turns sedative, leaving you dozing off before you know it. With these sleepy effects and its super high 20% + average THC level, Mantis is often chosen to treat those suffering from conditions such as chronic stress or PTSD, depression, insomnia and chronic fatigue. This bud has a sweet and spicy lemon-lime flavor, almost like a fresh Sprite. The aroma is very similar, although it does have hints of earthy herbs to it, too. Mantis buds have oversized heart-shaped blue-green nugs with dark amber hairs and a coating of blue-tinted white crystal trichomes.

Maple Syrup.name: Maple Syrup
Maple Syrup.description: Maple Syrup, also known as “Maple Leaf” or “Maple Leaf Indica,” is an extremely indica dominant hybrid (90% indica/10% sativa) strain created by crossing the classic Skunk #1 X Blue Black strains. It's called Maple Syrup for an apparent reason – it tastes exactly like what you'd expect! The flavor is very sweet and sugary with a notable vanilla undertone. The aroma takes a hit of citrus to the maple effect, mixing sharp orange with sweet sugary maple and adding a dash of spicy skunkiness that'll fill a room. And if you weren't hungry before smoking this bud, you'd better get some pancakes ready. The high definitely brings out a ravenous state of munchies that will leave you insatiable and dying for snacks. It starts first with a euphoric lift that leaves you feeling giddy and giggly, falling into bouts of uncontrollable laughter over almost anything and everything. A body stone comes next, pulling you into a hazy state before kicking in with the munchies. With these effects and its high average THC level of 17%, Maple Syrup is said to be perfect for treating nausea, appetite loss, chronic stress, and insomnia. This bud has piecey light minty green nugs with bright orange hairs and a coating of tiny white crystal trichomes that looks almost frosty.

Maple Wreck.name: Maple Wreck
Maple Wreck.description: Maple Wreck is a heavily sativa dominant hybrid strain (90% sativa/10% indica) created as a phenotype of the infamous Trainwreck strain. Named for its insanely delicious flavor, Maple Wreck packs tastes of sweet maple syrup and rich sugary woods into each and every toke. The aroma follows the same profile, although with a light touch of earth and herbs as the nugs are burned. The Maple Wreck high comes blasting in almost as soon as you exhale, launching your mind into a purely lifted state of heady euphoria. As your mind soars higher and higher, you'll start to feel an influx of creative energy and motivation with a touch of focus that will help you get going on any artistic undertakings that you have at hand. This effect does build without a ceiling, so mind your dosage if you're inclined to anxiety at all. Thanks to these hard-hitting effects and its high 18-25% average THC level, Maple Wreck is often chosen to treat those suffering from conditions such as chronic fatigue, ADD or ADHD, chronic stress, depression, mood swings, and chronic pain. This bud has long minty green spade-shaped nugs with thin clear amber hairs and a coating of sandy amber crystal trichomes dotted with sweet sticky resin.

Maraschino Cherry.name: Maraschino Cherry
Maraschino Cherry.description: Maraschino Cherry is an indica dominant hybrid strain (70% indica/30% sativa) created through crossing the delicious Kosher Tangie X Cherry Pie strains. Named for its mouthwatering flavor and celebrity parentage, Maraschino Cherry is the perfect choice for any fruity indica lover. Like its namesake treat, Maraschino Cherry has a sweet and fruity cherry flavor with a spicy yet sugary exhale. The aroma is of freshly picked spicy cherries with hints of earthy flowers and sharp menthol, too. The Maraschino Cherry high hits you just after your final toke, filling your mind with an expansive and heavy euphoria that leaves you with no room for any negative or racing thoughts. A sense of calm accompanies this happiness, filling your body with a soothing sense of relaxation. This combination can turn sedative, which will leave you dozing off before you realize what's happening. Thanks to these effects and its high 20-23% average THC level, Maraschino Cherry is often chosen to treat those suffering from conditions such as insomnia, depression, chronic pain, arthritis, muscle spasms or cramps and chronic stress. This bud has fat heart-shaped emerald green nugs with lots of thin light orange hairs and a coating of frosty, tiny golden white crystal trichomes.

Maraschino Gold.name: Maraschino Gold
Maraschino Gold.description: Maraschino Gold is an indica dominant hybrid strain (70% indica/30% sativa) created through crossing the delicious Kosher Tangie X Cherry Pie strains. Love the taste of maraschino cherries? This bud packs that and more into each and every tasty little toke. Maraschino Gold is said to have a flavor of sweet fruity cherries accented by touches of lightly sour citrus. The aroma follows the same profile, although with hints of skunkiness to it, too. The Maraschino Gold isn't quite as bright, with relaxing effects that start with a vibrancy before fading away. You'll feel an almost immediate rush of clear-headed focus and energy as soon as you experience your final tasty exhale, leaving you feeling lifted and motivated, ready to jump on anything from homework to household chores to a quick run around the block. While your mind is stimulated, your body will soon begin to drop away into a deeply calming state that keeps you slightly couch-locked and pain-free without causing too much sedation. Combine these effects with its high 16-19% THC level and you get the perfect tasty recipe for treating chronic fatigue, depression, ADD or ADHD, chronic stress and headaches or migraines. Maraschino Gold buds have fluffy popcorn-shaped minty green nugs with long thin orange hairs and tiny white trichomes.

Marathon OG.name: Marathon OG
Marathon OG.description: Marathon OG, also known as “Marathon Kush,” is an indica dominant hybrid strain created as a phenotype of the potent OG Kush strain. Made for rap superstar Nipsey Hu$$le and named after a series of his famous mix tapes, Marathon OG packs a heavy high that will lift you up mentally before knocking you flat on your back physically for hours and hours on end. The high starts in the head with a subtle euphoric build, lifting your spirits and giving you a touch of mental energy and focus. This quickly becomes fully overshadowed by a heavy, all-encompassing body high that knocks you flat down and locks you to the couch with a high level of potency. This quickly turns stoney and sedative, leaving you dozing off before you know it. With these effects and its high 20% + average THC level, Marathon OG is often chosen to treat conditions such as chronic fatigue, depression, chronic stress or anxiety, muscle spasms or cramps and chronic pain. This bud has a super spicy lemony earth flavor with a rich sour herbal aroma to match. Marathon OG buds have fluffy oversized popcorn-shaped minty green nugs with thick orange hairs interspersed throughout, light amber undertones and a frosty thick coating of tiny sparkling white crystal trichomes.

Margo Kush.name: Margo Kush
Margo Kush.description: Margo Kush is a rare evenly balanced hybrid strain (50% indica/50% sativa) created through crossing the classic Sour Diesel X OG Kush strains. Not to be confused with the like-named “Mango Kush,” this bud packs a super delicious sweet and sour lemon diesel flavor that will leave you begging for more. The aroma follows the same profile, with a citrusy pine overtone accented by savory diesel and sweet lemons as the nugs are burned. The Margo Kush high comes on soon after your first exhale, filling your mind with a lifted sense of calm and happiness that eases away any mental aches or pains with ease. Soon, a relaxing body high will begin to settle into your limbs, locking you to any couch or chair and leaving you in a state of pure happiness and ease. As both mind and body drift away, you'll start to feel pretty sleepy, dropping into a dozy state on and off as the high progresses before you finally pass out. Thanks to these effects and its super high 25% THC level, Margo Kush is often chosen to treat conditions such as depression, insomnia, chronic stress, chronic pain, and chronic fatigue. Margo Kush buds have fluffy dense grape-shaped forest green nugs with bright orange hairs and a coating of amber sandy crystal trichomes.

Marilyn Jane OG.name: Marilyn Jane OG
Marilyn Jane OG.description: Marilyn Jane OG, also known as “Marilyn Jane” or “Marilyn Jane Kush,” is a slightly indica dominant hybrid strain (60% indica/40% sativa) created through a three-way cross of the potent Mother's Finest X Juicy Fruit X AK-47 strains. This delicious combination yields a super-powered bud that is packed full of classic effects and a 24-28% THC level. The high has an almost immediate effect, hitting right between and behind the eyes almost as soon as you exhale with a buzzing energy. You'll suddenly feel laser-focused with a build in creativity and euphoria that has you jumping from mental task to mental task with ease. This buzzing will soon spread throughout the rest of your body, lulling you into a relaxed state that doesn't damper your mental energy too much. These effects with its high THC level make Marilyn Jane OG perfect for treating experienced patients suffering from conditions such as chronic pain, muscle spasms or cramps, migraines or headaches and chronic fatigue. Marilyn Jane OG has a classic strawberry diesel flavor with a heavily gassy and citrusy aroma to match. This bud has heart-shaped olive green nugs with dark orange hairs and a coating of tiny amber-tinted white crystal trichomes.

Marilyn Monroe.name: Marilyn Monroe
Marilyn Monroe.description: Marilyn Monroe, also known as “Marilyn Monroe OG,” is an indica dominant hybrid strain (70% indica/30% sativa) created through crossing the iconic JFK X Mother's Finest strains. Named for the iconic movie star, Marilyn Monroe is the perfect choice for any indica lover who's after a soothing high and a great flavor. This bud has a super sweet and fruity strawberry berry flavor with a light touch of woodiness upon exhale. The aroma is very similar, with a fruity strawberry overtone that's accented by earthy woody pine and hints of light pungency. The Marilyn Monroe high hits you almost as soon as you exhale, filling your mind with a lifted sense of happiness and ease. A physical sensation comes next, washing over your body in tingly waves, lulling you into a state of stimulating relaxation and ease. A sharp pang of hunger comes next, leaving you with a pretty hefty case of the munchies. In combination with its super high 27-33% average THC level, these effects make Marilyn Monroe a great choice for treating those suffering from conditions such as chronic pain, headaches or migraines, cramps or muscle spasms and nausea or appetite loss. This bud has fat heart-shaped emerald green nugs with dark orange hairs and a coating of tiny, milky white crystal trichomes.

Marmalade.name: Marmalade
Marmalade.description: Marmalade is a rare evenly balanced hybrid strain (50% indica/50% sativa) created through crossing the delicious Blueberry Cheesecake X Sour Tsunami strains. With Marmalade, the flavor is everything. This lovely lady packs a super sweet berry honey flavor into each and every toke. The aroma is a different story, with a rich skunky overtone that's accented by pungent cheese and herbs. The Marmalade high is one that's perfect for a lazy afternoon kicking back with friends or working on artistic undertakings. You'll feel a light touch of euphoria begin to build in the back of your mind after your first toke, turning quickly into a happy tingle that spreads from back to front, easing away any negative or racing thoughts. Soon, you'll feel an influx of creativity and energy fill your cerebral state, helping you to take on any artistic task on your to-do list with ease. With these effects and its high 12-23% average THC level and 1-6% CBD level, Marmalade is said to be perfect for treating those suffering from chronic stress, depression, mood swings, chronic fatigue, and nausea or appetite loss. This bud has oversized piecey bright yellow-green nugs with rich blue leaves, amber hairs, and a coating of matching glittery crystal trichomes.

marshmallow.name: marshmallow
marshmallow.description: Marshmallow is an indica dominant hybrid strain created through a cross of the classic OG Kush X an unknown strain. Although its second parent is unknown due to breeder secrecy, Marshmallow is thought to be a descendent of the Bubble Gum family because of its sickly sweet sugary flavor and mellow indica effects. Like its name suggests, Marshmallow has a super sweet candy flavor accented by nutty honey and a touch of fruitiness. The aroma is just as sweet, with a slightly pungent rotting marshmallow overtone that can be a little overwhelming to some upon exhaling. The Marshmallow high definitely hits the balanced hybrid sweet spot with indica heavy effects that are complemented by a nice cerebral high. It hits first in the forehead and behind the eyes with an uplifted euphoria that leaves you happy but totally hazy and a little out of it. As this high builds, it'll spread throughout the rest of your body in warming waves, leaving you with a tingly feeling from head to toe that numbs away any aches or pains. This will lull you into a state of complete relaxation, which pulls you down slowly into a hungry yet very sleepy state that almost always ends in a nice nap. Because of these effects and its moderate 14% average THC level, Marshmallow is perfect to treat insomnia, appetite loss, chronic pain, muscle spasms, and nausea. This bud has fluffy yet dense popcorn-shaped olive green nugs with rich purple undertones and hairs and a white frosty coating of milky crystal trichomes.

Mars OG Kush.name: Mars OG Kush
Mars OG Kush.description: This spacey indica-dominant hybrid is heavy on the body effects, perfect for late nights and dreary afternoons when little needs to be done. Mars OG is a California native out of the San Francisco Bay Area. A descendant of the original OG Kush, Marsh OG has a sativa/indica ratio of 20:80 and THC levels of up to 20%. That means an intense body high ideal for treating insomnia and other sleep disorders. CBD levels are relatively low, making this a less-than-ideal choice for disorders that respond to that form of cannabis therapy. This strain's extraterrestrial name is a reference to its status as a so-called "planetary" strain. These are marijuana strains that are planted indoors and later moved outdoors to complete the vegetative cycle. The smell is pungent and earthy, while the flavor is thick and fruity. This is a great choice for couch-lock and stress relief, as the body high is lazy and deeply relaxing. Feelings of euphoria and sleepiness are also common. Mars OG is best used to treat insomnia and anxiety, as well as chronic pain and appetite problems. Negative effects include dry mouth and red eyes, which are common, and paranoia and dizziness, which are not.

Martian Confidential.name: Martian Confidential
Martian Confidential.description: Martian Confidential is a super rare indica dominant hybrid strain created through crossing the potent Martian Mean Green with the infamous LA Confidential strain. User beware – Martian Confidential is not to be underestimated! With its insanely high THC level that bottoms out at about 20-21% and hard-hitting effects, this potent powerhouse can easily overwhelm even the most experienced of users. The high slams into you mere moments after your last toke, launching your mind into a hazy sense of relaxation and happiness. You'll feel yourself falling deeper and deeper into your own mind as your body is slowly taken over by a heavy stone. As you drift in and out of focus, your body will be pulled down further into deep sedation, leaving you immovable and incredibly sleepy. These effects in combination with its powerful THC level make Martian Confidential perfect for treating conditions such as chronic pain, insomnia, muscle spasms or tremors, arthritis, and depression. This bud has a dank spicy herbal flavor and a heavy pungent aroma to match. Martian Confidential buds have small round piecey olive green nugs with long thin amber hairs and a coating of clear crystal trichomes dotted with sweet sticky resin.

Martian Kush.name: Martian Kush
Martian Kush.description: Martian Kush is a slightly indica dominant hybrid (60% indica/40% sativa) strain created through crossing the classic Martian Mean Green X The OG #18 strains. With parents like these, it is no wonder Martian Kush is a patient favorite across the western side of the country. Martian Kush packs a hefty punch of giggly indica effects that are well balanced with an uplifted creative cerebral high. It starts with a building sense of euphoria that hits you first in the back of your head and builds through your very being, offering artistic inspiration and a surprising sense of calm. This head high is balanced beautifully by a building body buzz that is slightly tingly and leaves you completely relaxed, although very prone to falling into uncontrollable fits of giggles. Because of these effects and its powerful 18-19% average THC level, Martian Kush is said to be perfect for treating conditions such as chronic pain, muscle spasms, chronic pain, and appetite loss. This bud has lumpy popcorn-shaped olive green nugs with purple undertones, thin amber hairs, and a frosty lavender coating of crystal trichomes. Martian Kush packs a classic musky flavor of fruity earth with a tinge of berry and pungent kush. The aroma is very dank with a musky kush overtone and a hint of earthy berry as the nugs are broken apart.

Martian Muffin.name: Martian Muffin
Martian Muffin.description: Martian Muffin is a rare heavily indica dominant hybrid strain (90% indica/10% sativa) created through crossing the classic Girl Scout Cookies X Romulan strains. An out of this world flavor and lifted effects will be yours with this deliciously potent bud. Martian Muffin has a sweet and spicy nutty flavor with hints of rich citrus and slightly pungent pine upon exhale. The aroma is very earthy and sweet with a nutty citrus overtone that's almost like a fresh lemon cookie that's been left out in the sun for a little too long. The Martian Muffin high is super relaxing and lifted in nature, with fast-acting sleepy effects that are perfect for kicking back after a stressful day when sleep just won't seem to come. You'll feel lifted and relaxed with this high, with a sleepy overtone that leaves you dozing mere minutes after taking your first tasty toke. With these effects and its high 22-26% average THC level, Martian Muffin is said to be perfect for treating conditions such as chronic stress or anxiety, insomnia, headaches or migraines, depression, and appetite loss or nausea. This bud has huge oversized neon green nugs with turquoise, pink, and purple undertones with long red hairs and a coating of frosty white crystal trichomes.

Mary Chino.name: Mary Chino
Mary Chino.description: Mary Chino is a rare slightly sativa dominant hybrid strain (60% sativa/40% indica) created through crossing the infamous Cherry Pie X Tahoe Orange Tahoe strains. If you're in the market for a high-powered lady who will hit you hard with no mercy, Mary Chino is totally it. The Mary Chino high packs a wallop of body and cerebral effects that are best suited for a lazy afternoon when you don't have much of anything to do. The high starts with a lifted effect that fills your mind with a sense of unfocused and hazy euphoria that quickly turns dreamy and artistic. Soon, you'll begin to feel mentally sleepy as your body settles into a deep sense of relaxation and ease. In combination with its super high 22-26% average THC level, these potent effects give Mary Chino an edge in treating those suffering from conditions such as depression, migraines or headaches, mood swings, insomnia, and nausea or appetite loss. This bud has a sweet berry citrus flavor with a slightly pungent minty exhale that turns earthier the more you toke. The aroma is of pungent sour herbs and earth with a diesel berry overtone that quickly turns to heavy fuel as the nugs are broken apart and burned. Mary Chino buds have forest green dense arrowhead-shaped nugs with bright orange hairs and a thick frosty amber coating of crystal trichomes.

Maryhill Skunkberry.name: Maryhill Skunkberry
Maryhill Skunkberry.description: Merryhill Skunkberry, also known simply as “Blueberry Skunk,” is an indica dominant hybrid strain created through crossing the infamous DJ Short Blueberry X Skunk #1 strains. This bud is an in-house special for Merryhill, bred to capture a higher THC level than its classic Blueberry Skunk sister, bottoming out at 22% on average. This insanely high THC level powers a very cerebral head high that could definitely prove to be too much for any user who suffers from anxiety of any kind. The high starts with an almost immediate rushing euphoric effect that instantly boosts your mood and infuses you with a sense of energy. As your happiness builds and builds, your energy will ebb and bottom out, leaving you relaxed and lazy although incredibly blissful. This potent combination of effects and its high THC level make Merryhill Skunkberry ideal for treating experienced users who suffer from depression, chronic stress, chronic fatigue, mood swings, and migraines or tension headaches. This bud has a super sweet berry flavor accented by a strong punch of pungent skunkiness upon exhale that lingers long after you finish smoking. The stench is incredibly pungent with a powerful skunky berry effect that will fill any room. Merryhill Skunkberry buds have super dense conical forest green nugs with bright blue undertones, amber hairs, and a fine coating of tiny amber colored crystal trichomes.

Mary Jane.name: Mary Jane
Mary Jane.description: Mary Jane, also known as “Mary OG,” is an indica dominant hybrid strain that is a cross through OG Kush X an unknown high indica hybrid strain. Now you may think we're talking about MJ in general, but nope – there's an actual strain named after our favorite lady. Nevertheless, Mary Jane brings a classic flavor to the table, one that you'd expect from one with a name like this – sweet kush and spicy lemon accented by a touch of skunky earth. The aroma takes a pungent turn, with a dank kush effect and a punch of sour skunky lemon that can fill a room with its powerful stench. The Mary Jane high is definitely one to please, too, with powerful full-bodied effects that are both relaxing and uplifting in nature. It starts with a cerebral rush that hits you between the eyes and in the back of the head, numbing any mental pains instantly. As your mind falls into a happy uplifted state, your body will slowly become more and more relaxed, ending in a state of slight sedation that can end in sleep for the lesser experienced users. Coupled with its powerful THC level that typically bottoms out at 19%, these effects make Mary Jane perfect for taming the effects of mood swings, depression, irritability, and chronic pain. Mary Jane buds have small round piecey olive green nugs with furry amber hairs.

Mary OG.name: Mary OG
Mary OG.description: Mary OG, also known as “Mary Kush” or simply as “Mary,” is an indica dominant hybrid strain (70% indica/30% sativa) created through an unknown combination of indica strains. Even though its heritage is unknown, Mary OG is thought to be some sort of descendent of the famous OG Kush. That being said, the high is very similar to OG Kush, with full-bodied effects that start in the head before working their way throughout the rest of your body. You'll feel a tingly sense of growing euphoria at the onset of the high, filling you with a sense of well-being and a touch of sociable energy. As you find yourself carrying on conversations with those around you, a giggly sense will wash over you, leaving you laughing at anything and everything. The tingle will soon turn into a heavy buzz, leaving you fully relaxed and pretty aroused at times. Combined with its high 18-21% average THC level, these effects make Mary OG perfect for treating chronic stress, depression, appetite loss or nausea and chronic pain. This bud has a classic sweet and spicy flavor with a delicious flowery and earthy aroma to match. Mary OG buds have fluffy oversized spade-shaped forest green nugs with thin orange hairs and a frosty thick coating of chunky bright white crystal trichomes.

Master Hemp.name: Master Hemp
Master Hemp.description: Master Hemp is a rare sativa dominant hybrid strain (70% sativa/30% indica) created as a cross of the infamous CBD-1 X Swiss Line strains. Searching for a super medicinal high to help ease your day-to-day aches and pains? Look no further – Master Hemp totally has you covered. This baby packs a super relaxing and clear-headed high that almost instantly kills the effects of a wide variety of conditions without any psychedelic effects, especially considering its 0% THC level and super high 12-16% average CBD level. You’ll feel lifted and totally relaxed with a sense of mental clarity that lends itself well to any task at hand. This is all accented by a touch of focus and motivation that won’t cause any anxiety or paranoia in the slightest. Thanks to these mellow effects, Master Hemp is said to be the perfect highly medicinal strain for treating conditions such as inflammation, spasticity, autism, chronic pain, glaucoma or headaches and nausea or appetite loss. This bud has a classic sweet tropical citrus flavor with a lightly sour herbal exhale. The aroma is of fruity earth and sour citrus with an herbal overtone that becomes slightly spicy as the nugs are broken apart and burned. Master Hemp buds have oversized airy spade-shaped olive green nugs with rich purple undertones, dark amber hairs and a coating of dark frosty purple crystal trichomes.

Master Kush Diesel.name: Master Kush Diesel
Master Kush Diesel.description: Master Kush Diesel is one of the most renowned indica strains in the marijuana world. This strain's origin will lead you back to the Hindu Kush region where many other prominent indicas have emanated. Master Kush is an 100% indica hybrid that is a cross between Hindu Kush and Skunk. You should not smoke Master Kush if you're anticipating a very busy day or one that requires a great amount of focus. This strain delivers an almost immediate, relaxing body high that comes complete with acute mental clarity; something that is not common amongst other Indica strains. While the initial high can be full of socially elevated spirits, you'll eventually settle down to a deep and relaxing sleep. Patients often choose Master Kush due to it's ability to alleviate stress, pain, depression and insomnia. In the looks department, master kush produces distinguishable ball-shaped buds covered in bright orange hairs. In addition, it's character look, you will encounter a very strong citrus aroma with a hint of pine. Upon smoking, you can anticipate a pleasant and smooth taste that miraculously mimics its smell.

Master Miyagi Og.name: Master Miyagi Og
Master Miyagi Og.description: Master Miyagi OG, also known as “Master Miyagi” or “Miyagi OG,” is an indica dominant hybrid strain (80% indica/20% sativa) created through crossing the infamous Hindu Kush X Skunk strains. This powerhouse celebrity child packs a potent punch of effects that will knock you flat out thanks to its super high 25-27% average THC level. That being said, Master Miyagi OG is one bud that you shouldn't underestimate. The high comes on fast and hard, with cerebral effects that send you flying into a hazy state of unfocused euphoria. Soon, your body will fall victim to his potency, dropping off into a deeply relaxing physical state that leaves you slightly couch-locked and totally at ease with the world around you. These full-bodied effects quickly turn sedative, leaving you sleepy and dozing off and on for hours on end. In combination with its high THC level, these heavy effects give Master Miyagi OG an edge in treating conditions such as chronic pain, depression, insomnia, and muscle spasms or cramps. This bud has a skunky herbal flavor with a slightly sour earthy exhale. The aroma is of pungent sour earth and heavy dank skunk with a touch of spiciness as the nugs are broken apart and burned. Master Miyagi OG buds have spade-shaped forest green nugs with amber furry hairs and a coating of frosty thick amber crystal trichomes.

Master P.name: Master P
Master P.description: Master P, also known as “MasterP,” is a rare 100% indica hybrid strain created through crossing the classic Master Kush X an unknown combination of indica strains. Known for its insanely potent high, Master P is perfect for any indica lover who wants a little power behind their high. The high starts with a lazy feeling that slowly washes over you and builds into a slow burn, keeping you totally couch-locked and slightly sedated. A calming body high accompanies this heavy physical state, lifting you into pure bliss and ease. A buzzing feeling comes next, dropping your body into full sedation and leaving you dozing before you know it. With these effects and its high 20-25% average THC level, Master P is often chosen to treat those suffering from conditions such as chronic stress, depression, nausea, insomnia and chronic pain. This bud has a classic spicy flowery flavor with a harsh peppery exhale that can leave you coughing. The aroma is of peppery herbs and flowery earth with a lightly sweet overtone that turns spicier and spicier the more that you toke. Master P buds have popcorn-shaped forest green nugs with lots of thin amber hairs and a thick frosty coating of tiny matching crystal trichomes.

Master Permafrost.name: Master Permafrost
Master Permafrost.description: Master Permafrost is an indica dominant hybrid strain created through a cross of the potent Master Kush X Permafrost strains. This bud takes the character and appearance of Permafrost and multiplies them times a billion. The appearance is what you'll notice about it first – it has oversized super dense grape-shaped dark olive green nugs with amber hairs and a coating of tiny crystal trichomes that glitter in the light. The scent comes next, with a heavy pungency that's still fragrant and floral although skunky and woody. Once you take a hit of Master Permafrost, you'll taste sweet smooth flavors of pine and citrus that are surprisingly mellow in nature and very pleasant overall. The Master Permafrost high is a full-bodied experience that everyone should have at least once in their lives. It hits you first with a punch of euphoria and focus that leaves you feeling like you can conquer the world with ease. As your head high builds, your focus will suddenly wane, leaving you stoney and hazy with no hope of concentrating on anything. A sleepy effect will eventually wash over both mind and body, leaving you sedated and utterly relaxed. With its high 17-22% THC level and heavy-hitting effects, Master Permafrost is perfect for treating conditions such as ADD/ADHD, chronic pain, insomnia, and headaches or migraines.

Master Purple.name: Master Purple
Master Purple.description: Master Purple is an indica dominant hybrid strain (70% indica/30% sativa) created through crossing the classic Master Kush X Purple Kush strains. This celebrity child is best known for its super potent high thanks to its heavy 20-24% average THC level and totally gorgeous appearance. Master Purple buds have dense grape-shaped bright neon green nugs with lots of thin yellow-orange hairs and a coating of golden amber crystal trichomes. As you pull apart each frosty little nugget, aromas of pungent grape and spicy berries are released with a touch of dank herbs as the nugs are burned. The flavor is of fresh grape and earth with a touch of spicy berries and rich herbs upon exhale. The Master Purple high is just as mouthwatering as the flavor, with long-lasting effects that will actually leave you feeling slightly energized, even with its indica dominance. It starts with a lift of the spirits, infusing you with a sense of happiness and ease that fills you with pure euphoria. A touch of mental energy accompanies this lift, leaving your mind active while your body settles into deep relaxation and peace. Thanks to these effects and its high THC level, Master Purple is perfect for treating chronic pain, insomnia, appetite loss or nausea, and chronic stress.

Masters'N Crime.name: Masters'N Crime
Masters'N Crime.description: Masters ‘N Crime, also known as “Masters & Crime” or “Masters N Crime,” is an indica dominant hybrid strain (80% indica/20% sativa) created through crossing the classic Super Bud X (Jack Herer X Himalayan Gold) strains. If you're after a soothing bud that will help you settle down and relax before getting to sleep at night, you've found it with Masters ‘N Crime. It starts with a subtle boost that creeps into the brain and body, filling it with a lightly weighty happy sense that pushes out any negative or racing thoughts. You'll feel a sense of calm accompany this euphoric boost, helping you to settle down without any aches or pains to speak of. A sharp pang of hunger comes next, leaving you reaching for anything in sight to snack on. Combined with its super high 20-30% average THC level, these full-bodied effects make Masters ‘N Crime a great choice for treating those patients suffering from conditions such as chronic pain, depression, chronic stress, appetite loss or nausea and insomnia. This bud has a sweet and sour citrusy lemon flavor with a lightly spicy and flowery exhale. The aroma is very similar, with a woody flowery overtone accented by spicy herbs and fresh fruity citrus. Masters ‘N Crime buds have heavy conical forest green nugs with thick amber hairs and a frosty milky coating of tiny, amber tinted crystal trichomes.

Master Tuna.name: Master Tuna
Master Tuna.description: Master Tuna, also known as “Master Tuna Kush,” is an indica dominant hybrid strain (70% indica/30% sativa or 75% indica/25% sativa) created through crossing the classic Master Kush X Tuna Kush strains. This celebrity child boasts a super stimulating high that surprisingly hits a lot like a sativa rather than an indica. You'll feel an immediate increase in sensory awareness, filling your mind with a sense of thoughtful energy that goes well with your sharpened focus. You'll feel creative and inspired, ready to tackle anything on your to-do list. As your mind continues to sharpen, your body will start to fall off into a heavy relaxation that leaves you slightly sedated without causing too much sedation. Combined with its high 18-23% THC level, these full-bodied effects give Master Tuna an edge in treating conditions such as chronic fatigue, depression, chronic stress, arthritis, insomnia and chronic pain. Master Tuna has a classic spicy fishy pungent flavor with a super sour citrusy exhale. The aroma is heavier and more pungent than the taste, with hints of rotting fish and skunk that fill any room with a heavy stench. Master Tuna buds have oversized spade-shaped minty green nugs with amber undertones, lots of orange hairs and a coating of tiny golden amber crystal trichomes.

Master x Blackberry.name: Master x Blackberry
Master x Blackberry.description: Master x Blackberry is basically an indica strain that is a made of Blackberry and Afghani strains. It comprises of striking dark purple buds that have orange hairs. The plant of this strain takes up to 7-8 weeks to blossom. It usually does not have high yields but its buds are dense and contain crystals. This specific strain has a strong, fuel-like smell and a balanced taste because of sweet berries. People have varied responses regarding the smell of Master x Blackberry but most agree on its taste and describe it as being sweet and fruity. It carries a flavor similar to that of eucalyptus leaves and is generally described as being smooth on the throat. The ancestry of the Master x Blackberry strain is a mystery. It has been popular especially in the dispensaries of California. Due to the fact that it is able to induce the body effects that can be attributed to the dominant indica gene, this strain is highly recommended for trying dealing with pain. It can be called a night time strain as it helps relax the body and induces sleep. It provides a relaxing effect to the user. Due to this, it is effective for people suffering from insomnia and pain but should not be consumed in the mornings as it can make a person tired and lazy.

Matanuska Mint.name: Matanuska Mint
Matanuska Mint.description: Matanuska Mint is an evenly balanced hybrid (50% sativa/50% indica) strain created as a cross of the delicious Matanuska Thunder X Gray Mist strains. This bud is named for its infamous minty taste and smell, and offers the user a moderate THC level between 14-16%. Both the aroma and taste have a sharp minty hit that transition into a deliciously smooth earthy spice. Matanuska Mint buds have long narrow cigar-shaped forest green nugs with a spattering of long thin minty hairs and minty undertones. Each nug is frosted with a fine layer of sugary white trichomes and sweet sticky resin. The Matanuska Mint high hits you hard and fast with a case of red droopy eyes and a hazy mind that is accompanied by a quickly building cerebral energy and motivation. This sativa based high will keep building as the high continues, outweighing the body effects completely until the comedown. As the high starts to fade, the body high will take hold and leave you completely sedated and couch-locked with an overwhelming sleepiness that will eventual knock you out cold. Because of these effects, Matanuska Mint is perfect for treating asthma, chronic pain, fatigue, and mild to moderate cases of depression.

Matanuskan Mist.name: Matanuskan Mist
Matanuskan Mist.description: Matanuskan Mist, also known as “Matanuska Mist,” is a sativa dominant hybrid strain created through crossing the infamous Matanuska Tundra X Grey Mist strains. Named for both of its parent strains, this celebrity child packs a super heavy high that will have you totally couch-locked and kicking back for hours on end. It starts with a subtle lift that fills you with a cerebral happiness that's accented by energy and focus. A deeply relaxing body buzz comes next, washing over you in warming waves and leaving you totally couch-locked and immovable for hours and hours on end. With these effects and its high 15-16% average THC level, Matanuskan Mist is said to be perfect for treating those suffering from conditions such as chronic stress, depression, chronic pain, mood swings and ADD or ADHD. This bud has a rich spicy herbal overtone with an earthy effect that turns pungent almost as soon as it hits the tongue. The aroma is of earthy pungency with a heavy skunky overtone that turns dank and spicy as the nugs are burned away. Matanuskan Mist buds have dense grape-shaped dusty green nugs with thin light amber hairs and a dusty coating of thick frosty amber crystal trichomes.

Matanuska Thunder.name: Matanuska Thunder
Matanuska Thunder.description: Matanuska Thunder, also known as “Matanuska Thunder Fuck,” “Matanuskan Thunder” and “Matanuska Thunderfuck,” is a slightly sativa dominant hybrid strain (60% sativa/40% indica) created through an unknown combination of hybrid strains. Infamous for its super lazy high, Matansuka Thunder is the perfect bud for when you need a little extra help to really kick back and relax after a long and stressful day. You'll feel a lifted state of euphoria come rushing in first, filling your mind with pure happiness and a touch of giggly creativity. As your mind reaches new heights, your body will begin to settle into a deeply relaxing state that keeps you couch-locked and anchored. In combination with its high 13-16% average THC level and 1-2% CBD level, these effects give Matanuska Thunder an edge in treating those suffering from conditions such as chronic stress, nausea, chronic pain, depression and chronic fatigue. This bud has a super sweet chocolaty flavor with a lightly spicy earthy exhale. The aroma is of earthy herbs and spicy chocolate with a rich dark chocolate overtone that sweetens as the nugs are burned away. Matanuska Thunder buds have small thick heart-shaped bright neon green nugs with lots of orange hairs, bright amber undertones and a matching coating of crystal trichomes.
